{"name":"Harrier Style","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"Any martial class","source":"feat","category":"Ranged Style","benefit":"When you hit with a ranged weapon attack against a creature adjacent to at least one of your allies, it is flatfooted against the next attack which targets it before the end of your next turn.","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Property","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"8M0nFvJ7lB5VNJ5L"}
{"name":"Guardian Style","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"Any martial class","source":"feat","category":"Melee Style","benefit":"While you are wielding a shield, the shieldâ€™s bonus to AC and Reflex also applies to your Fortitude. When you hit with an attack that has the Shield keyword, the target suffers disfavor on attack rolls against you until the end of your next turn. ","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Property","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"B15ssrPrlG4QCkQG"}
{"name":"Dervish Style","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"Any martial class","source":"feat","category":"Melee Style","benefit":"While you are wielding two melee weapons, you gain a +2 bonus to AC and Reflex against melee attacks. When you make a normal melee attack with your main-hand weapon, you may choose to make a normal melee attack with your off-hand weapon at the same time. If you choose to do so, both attacks deal only half damage.","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Property","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"GQgoP4ANjoU7OoWU"}
{"name":"Barrage Style","permission":{"default":0,"hsFJxrWN4M5Ezw3L":3},"type":"feature","data":{"description":"","req":"Any martial class","source":"feat","category":"Ranged Style","benefit":"When you make a ranged weapon attack which targets multiple creatures within a set number of squares of each other, you may increase the distance allowed between targets by 2 squares.","notes":"","sources":{"rfeature":{"label":"Racial Feature","value":"rfeature"},"cfeature":{"label":"Class Feature","value":"cfeature"},"ifeature":{"label":"Item Property","value":"ifeature"},"feat":{"label":"Feat","value":"feat"},"prof":{"label":"Proficiency","value":"prof"},"other":{"label":"Other","value":"other"}}},"flags":[],"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"IYRhctU0w01gBTmb"}
